	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In the NTSC version, one version has him end up next to a pipe, while the other one kills him. Both times he successfully collects the mushroom.
<br />
<br />In the PAL version of SMB1, the demo always results in Mario dying. Both times, he fails to hit the [?] block to release the mushroom. This is because the physics were altered for the PAL version, but the demo sequence was unchanged.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


